text.tspan: ReaderAI is a powerful Chrome extension designed to enhance the
browsing experience of users. With ReaderAI, you can effortlessly extract
essential text from webpages, making it easier to gather and organize
crucial information. This feature proves invaluable when conducting
research, studying, or simply gathering insights.
Additionally, ReaderAI offers a remarkable text assist feature that
significantly streamlines your workflow. Say goodbye to manual note-
taking and tedious information management. ReaderAI empowers users
with intelligent tools, allowing for seamless text extraction, efficient note
organization, and a more productive online experience.
